---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Nederlandse Wetgeving E-Bikes | E-Bike Database NL" description="Wetgeving voor e-bikes, bromfietsen en e-crossers in Nederland.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 text-white py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Nederlandse Wetgeving</h1>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90">E-bikes en elektrische crossers op de Nederlandse weg</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-10">
      <table class="w-full bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <thead class="bg-blue-600 text-white"><tr><th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Categorie</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Max km/h</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Rijbewijs</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Kenteken</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Helm</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Fietspad</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200 text-sm">
          <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">E-bike</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">25</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-green-600">Nee</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-green-600">Nee</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-green-600">Nee</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-green-600">Ja</td></tr>
          <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Speed Pedelec</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">45</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-green-600">Nee</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Blauw</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Ja</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Nee*</td></tr>
          <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Snorfiets (L1e-A)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">25</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">AM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Blauw</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-orange-500">Deels**</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-orange-500">Deels</td></tr>
          <tr class="bg-orange-50 hover:bg-orange-100"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold">Bromfiets (L1e-B)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">45</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">AM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Geel</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Ja</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Nee</td></tr>
          <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Motorfiets (L3e)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">&gt;45</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">A1/A2/A</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Ja</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Ja</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-red-600">Nee</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">* Snelfietspad (F-route) wel toegestaan &nbsp;|&nbsp; ** Helm verplicht in Amsterdam, Rotterdam, Den Haag, Utrecht op fietspad</p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-5 rounded-r-lg"><h2 class="font-bold text-orange-800 mb-2">Bromfiets (L1e-B) â€” de meeste e-crossers</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Surron, Talaria, Segway X260 en vergelijkbare modellen begrensd op 45 km/h. AM rijbewijs + geel kenteken + WA-verzekering + helm verplicht. Niet op het fietspad. Voertuig moet Europese L1e-B typegoedkeuring hebben.</p></div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-5 rounded-r-lg"><h2 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">Speed Pedelec</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">45 km/h met trapondersteuning. Geen rijbewijs nodig (gewijzigd 2017), maar blauw kenteken, WA-verzekering en helm verplicht. Niet op regulier fietspad, wel op snelfietspad (F-route).</p></div>
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-5 rounded-r-lg"><h2 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-2">Motorfiets (L3e) â€” KTM Freeride, Zero FX</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-700">A1 rijbewijs (tot 11kW), A2 (tot 35kW, bijv. KTM 18kW) of A (onbeperkt, bijv. Zero FX 34kW). Motorfiets APK, verzekering en goedgekeurde motorhelm verplicht.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg"><h2 class="font-bold mb-2">Kenteken aanvragen (RDW)</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Conformiteitsverklaring (CoC), aankoopbewijs en identiteitsbewijs nodig. Kosten ca. â‚¬20.</p><a href="https://www.rdw.nl/particulier/voertuigen/bromfiets-snorfiets/nieuw-voertuig-kentekenen" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700">RDW.nl â†’</a></div>
  </div>
</Layout>
